title: Reaching the Finish Line with JD Vance and Blake Masters
itunes:title: Reaching the Finish Line with JD Vance and Blake Masters
description:
JD Vance and Blake Masters are two of the most important, innovative conservative candidates in the midterms. Both of them are battling fake moderates who are in lockstep with Democrat leaders on everything important. And today, both of them join Charlie to talk about closing strong and making sure the crucial Ohio and Arizona Senate races are a victory for Republicans.

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
